text: Bagumbayan can refer to: ;Places in the Philippines * Bagumbayan, Sultan Kudarat, a municipality * Bagumbayan Field, old name of Rizal Park, Manila * Bagumbayan, Quezon City, a barangay in Quezon City, Eastern Manila District * Bagumbayan, Taguig, a barangay in Southern Manila District * Bagumbayan North, a barangay in Navotas, Northern Manila District * Bagumbayan South, a barangay in Navotas, Northern Manila District ;Other * Bagumbayan–Volunteers for a New Philippines (Bagumbayan-VNP), a political party in the Philippines
title: Bagumbayan
